[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
2 oz [genericingredient Brandy] Don Pedro Brandy
1/2 oz [genericingredient Peppermint Schnapps] Hiram Walker Peppermint Schnapps
1/2 oz [genericingredient White Cr De Cacao] Hiram Walker White Cr De Cacao
1/2 oz Sweet/Sour Mix
Shake and Strain
Top: Club Soda
Garnish: Mint Sprig

